mono_direct
-----------

l1: $ mono f , (f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta) ÔŐó mono f $ by ax (g := $ f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta $, a := $ mono f $) []
l2: $ mono f , (f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta) ÔŐó ÔłÇ y ((f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś y) Ôćĺ (alpha ~ y)) $ by all_elim [l1]
l3: $ mono f , (f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta) ÔŐó (f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta) Ôćĺ (alpha ~ beta) $ by all_elim [l2]
l4: $ mono f , (f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta) ÔŐó f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta $ by ax (g := $ mono f $, a := $ f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta $) []
l5: $ mono f , (f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta) ÔŐó alpha ~ beta $ by imp_elim (g := $ mono f , (f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta) $, h := $ mono f , (f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta) $, a := $ f Ôłś alpha ~ f Ôłś beta $, b := $ alpha ~ beta $) [l3, l4]

pullback_eq_direct
------------------

l1: $ pullback f g h k ÔŐó pullback f g h k $ by ax (g := $ emp $, a := $ pullback f g h k $) []
l2: $ pullback f g h k ÔŐó f Ôłś h ~ g Ôłś k $ by and_elim_l [l1]

pullback_use_direct
-------------------

l1: $ pullback f g h k ÔŐó pullback f g h k $ by ax (g := $ emp $, a := $ pullback f g h k $) []
l2: $ pullback f g h k ÔŐó ÔłÇ x ÔłÇ y ÔłÇ z ((f Ôłś x ~ g Ôłś y) Ôćĺ ((h Ôłś z ~ x) Ôćĺ ((k Ôłś z ~ y) Ôćĺ (z ~ pb_med f g h k x y)))) $ by and_elim_r [l1]
l3: $ pullback f g h k ÔŐó ÔłÇ y ÔłÇ z ((f Ôłś a ~ g Ôłś y) Ôćĺ ((h Ôłś z ~ a) Ôćĺ ((k Ôłś z ~ y) Ôćĺ (z ~ pb_med f g h k a y)))) $ by all_elim [l2]
l4: $ pullback f g h k ÔŐó ÔłÇ z ((f Ôłś a ~ g Ôłś b) Ôćĺ ((h Ôłś z ~ a) Ôćĺ ((k Ôłś z ~ b) Ôćĺ (z ~ pb_med f g h k a b)))) $ by all_elim [l3]
l5: $ pullback f g h k ÔŐó (f Ôłś a ~ g Ôłś b) Ôćĺ ((h Ôłś u ~ a) Ôćĺ ((k Ôłś u ~ b) Ôćĺ (u ~ pb_med f g h k a b))) $ by all_elim [l4]

mono_pullback_step
------------------

l1: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó mono f $ by ax (g := $ pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) $, a := $ mono f $) []
l2: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó ÔłÇ y ((f Ôłś (h Ôłś alpha) ~ f Ôłś y) Ôćĺ (h Ôłś alpha ~ y)) $ by all_elim [l1]
l3: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó (f Ôłś (h Ôłś alpha) ~ f Ôłś (h Ôłś beta)) Ôćĺ (h Ôłś alpha ~ h Ôłś beta) $ by all_elim [l2]
l4: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó pullback f g h k $ by ax (g := $ mono f , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) $, a := $ pullback f g h k $) []
l5: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó f Ôłś h ~ g Ôłś k $ by and_elim_l [l4]
l6: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó f Ôłś (h Ôłś alpha) ~ g Ôłś (k Ôłś alpha) $ by comp_right [l5]
l7: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó f Ôłś (h Ôłś beta) ~ g Ôłś (k Ôłś beta) $ by comp_right [l5]
l8: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta $ by ax (g := $ mono f , pullback f g h k $, a := $ k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta $) []
l9: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó g Ôłś (k Ôłś alpha) ~ g Ôłś (k Ôłś beta) $ by comp_left [l8]
l10: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó f Ôłś (h Ôłś alpha) ~ g Ôłś (k Ôłś beta) $ by mor_trans (g := $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) $, f := $ f Ôłś (h Ôłś alpha) $, h := $ g Ôłś (k Ôłś alpha) $, i := $ g Ôłś (k Ôłś beta) $) [l6, l9]
l11: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó g Ôłś (k Ôłś beta) ~ f Ôłś (h Ôłś beta) $ by mor_sym (g := $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) $, f := $ f Ôłś (h Ôłś beta) $, h := $ g Ôłś (k Ôłś beta) $) [l7]
l12: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó f Ôłś (h Ôłś alpha) ~ f Ôłś (h Ôłś beta) $ by mor_trans (g := $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) $, f := $ f Ôłś (h Ôłś alpha) $, h := $ g Ôłś (k Ôłś beta) $, i := $ f Ôłś (h Ôłś beta) $) [l10, l11]
l13: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) ÔŐó h Ôłś alpha ~ h Ôłś beta $ by imp_elim (g := $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) $, h := $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k Ôłś alpha ~ k Ôłś beta) $, a := $ f Ôłś (h Ôłś alpha) ~ f Ôłś (h Ôłś beta) $, b := $ h Ôłś alpha ~ h Ôłś beta $) [l3, l12]
